   The U.S. Geological Survey (USGS) Branch of Quality Systems (BQS)
   welcomes you to our web site.  We hope that you find our web page easy
   to navigate and the information useful.  Some of our information is for
   internal USGS use only and will not be accessible,  if you need
   additional information on this web page please contact the Webmaster.
     __________________________________________________________________

    Branch Of Quality Systems Mission - Science requires consistent
   collection and reporting of known quality data
     * Monitor, assure, and improve the quality of analytical results
     * Documentation of field and laboratory methods
     * Proficiency Testing
          + Internal and external quality control
          + Single and double blind samples
     * Documentation of variability and bias of analytical results for:
          + District Users
          + Laboratory Personnel
          + Multiple use and long-term trends
     * Documentation of analytical methods used for:
          + Inorganic Constituents
          + Organic Constituents
          + Biological Constituents
   __________________________________________________________________

